high_descs: Turn left head to the counter on the left side of the stove
Pick up the bread knife on the counter
Turn right walk forward then head to the right side of the  stove counter
Slice the tomato behind the bread
Look down the bread on the counter
Put the knife on top of the bread
Move forward then look at the tomato
Pick up a slice tomato
Turn left then head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in and out the tomato then close the fridge
Turn right then head to the microwave
Open the microwave and put in the slice tomato
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled tomato in the microwave

high_descs: Go forward, turn right after the stove
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn right, go forward, turn left after the stove
Slice the tomato on the counter
Turn down to the counter
Put the knife on the counter
Turn up to the counter
Pick up a tomato slice from the counter
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the fridge
Put the tomato slice in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the tomato slice from the microwave
Turn right, go forward, turn right and go to the microwave
Put the tomato slice in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato, cool a slice, put it in the microwave

high_descs: Turn and face the counter on your right.
Pick up the knife on the counter between the cabbage and sponge.
Head right and then turn to face the counter on your left.
Slice the tomato on the counter behind the loaf of bread.
Look down to the counter while holding the knife.
Leave the knife on top of the loaf of bread.
Look up towards the counter.
Pick up one tomato slice from the counter.
Head left towards the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and place the tomato on the middle shelf and shut the door.  After a brief pause open the refrigerator door again and pick up the tomato slice and shut the door again.
Turn around and cross the kitchen and approach the sink.
Place the slice of tomato onto the plate inside the microwave that is above the sink and shut the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Retrieve a cold slice of tomato and put it into the microwave.
